title: Seeing Double
short_desc: The crew lands on a planet only to be ambushed by an enemy team of bounty hunters.

Can sssomeone get thisss guy off me?

I am terribly sorry for my behavior last night. I have no idea what I was thinking, drinking with strangers.

Seth jumps the ship to another asteroid, "hopping" it to and fro haphazardly.
Asier manages to hand a water to Iris before nearly toppling over from Seth's piloting.
